sick.) 3 So the sisters sent
word to Jesus, “Lord, behold,
the one yoʋ love is sick.”
4 But when Jesus heard this,
he said, “This sickness will
not end in death but is
for the glory of God, so
that the Son of God may
be glorified through it.”
5 Now Jesus loved Martha,
her sister, and Lazarus.
6 But when he heard that
