13
The Way of Love
1 If I speak in the tongues
of men and of angels, but
do not have love, I am a
noisy gong or a clanging
2 If I have the
cymbal.
gift of prophecy and know
all mysteries and all knowl-
edge, and if I have all faith,
so as to move mountains,
but do not have love, I am
nothing. 3 If I give away
