be teachers by this time,
you need someone to teach
you again the basic princi-
ples of the oracles of God.
You need milk, not solid
food. 13 Anyone who lives
on milk is unacquainted
with the teaching about righ-
teousness, for he is an in-
fant. 14 But solid food is for
the mature, whose faculties
have been trained by prac-
tice to distinguish between
good and evil.
6
Warning Against Falling
Away
1 Therefore, let us leave
behind
the
elementary
teaching about Christ and
