The Meaning of Faith
faith is the assur-
ance of what we hope for
and the conviction of what
we do not see. 2 Because of
their faith, the people of old
were commended.
3 By faith we understand
that the universe was
formed by the word of God,
so that what is seen was not
made out of what is visible.
