The Discipline of the Lord
1 Therefore, since we have
such a great cloud of wit-
nesses surrounding us, let
us lay aside every weight
and the sin that so easily
entangles us, and let us run
with endurance the race that
lies before us, 2 fixing our
eyes upon Jesus, the author
